# Changelog

## v0.0.1 - April 30, 2025

- Project initialized
- Temperature and humidity logging
- Basic web server and dashboard

## v1.0.0_refactored - 2025-06-02

- Major refactoring to comply with PRD requirements
- Removed hardcoded credentials (moved to config.h)
- Fixed Supabase data structure (removed nested "data" object)
- Changed endpoint from /water to /water-now
- Removed legacy files (data/, backup files, backend/)
- Improved code modularity and separation of concerns
- Updated frontend to handle flat data structure
- Added proper error handling and status codes
